Hello.
 We’ve created theme. When I send theme to another account I’ve got warning (first screen) in page editor  (second screen). Anyone had issue like that? On account where theme is, everything is okay, some problem with sending player_id. Any ideas?

Hey <@U025M7ZCEBH>! My guess here is that it’s an issue with the default video for your video field. To my knowledge, in the HubSpot File Manager, the video gets assigned an ID, and it may not be consistent from account to account. If you try a different default video, does the error resolve?
Hey <@U02NJACH5QS>. I thought so too … We’ve got feedback from HubSpot that we have warning in this module (HubSpot challange 2022) and we need to solve it xD
